@StarterApp_Api_HostAddress = http://localhost:5164

### Public liveness smoke test (no gateway identity required)
GET {{StarterApp_Api_HostAddress}}/health/live
Accept: application/json

###

# Protected /api/v1 routes run behind a trusted gateway (APIM). The gateway projects the
# normalized identity headers below and, in production-like mode, a signed X-Gateway-Assertion.
# Calling these routes directly from this scratch file will return 401 unless those headers are
# present and valid. This example documents the required contract; supply real gateway-issued
# values (or run via the gateway) to exercise it.
GET {{StarterApp_Api_HostAddress}}/api/v1/products
Accept: application/json
X-Correlation-ID: 11111111-1111-1111-1111-111111111111
X-Authenticated-Subject: sample-subject
X-Authenticated-Principal-Type: user
X-Authenticated-Tenant-Id: sample-tenant
X-Authenticated-Scopes: products:read

###
